<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Data Scientist Portfolio</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.plotly.com/plotly-latest.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0d0d0d;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0f0f0f, #1b1b1b);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .headshot {
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 2px solid cyan;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: cyan;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px cyan;
        }
        nav a {
            margin: 0 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: cyan;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: relative;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px cyan;
        }
        nav a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            bottom: -5px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: cyan;
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        nav a:hover::after {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }
        .container {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .project {
            margin: 40px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid cyan;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .project:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.4);
        }
        .project h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: cyan;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px cyan;
        }
        .project p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #cccccc;
        }
        .plot {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border: 2px solid cyan;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #101010;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            background: #0f0f0f;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            border-top: 2px solid cyan;
        }
        footer a {
            color: cyan;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        footer a:hover {
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px cyan;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class=\"title\">Data Scientist Portfolio</div>
        <img class=\"headshot\" src=\"headshot.jpg\" alt=\"Professional Headshot\">
        <nav>
            <a href=\"#projects\">Projects</a>
            <a href=\"https://github.com/your-github\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <div class=\"container\">
        <section id=\"projects\">
            <h2 style=\"color: cyan; text-align: center; text-shadow: 0 0 10px cyan;\">Projects</h2>
            <div class=\"project\">
                <h3>Project 1: Interactive Visualization</h3>
                <p>Details about this project.</p>
                <div id=\"plot1\" class=\"plot\"></div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>Â© 2025 Your Name | <a href=\"https://github.com/your-github\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a></p>
    </footer>
    <script>
        function createPlot(id) {
            Plotly.newPlot(id, [{ x: [1, 2, 3, 4], y: [10, 15, 13, 17], mode: 'lines+markers', marker: { color: 'cyan' }}], { margin: { t: 0 }, paper_bgcolor: '#101010', plot_bgcolor: '#101010', font: { color: '#e0e0e0' }});\n           }\n           createPlot('plot1');\n       </script>\n   </body>\n   </html>\n   ```

